data.description: This wonderfully well kept single family home in Norfolk is a great opportunity to own in a conveniently located neighborhood a short distance to downtown, NSU, ODU, Military bases and the interstate. You'll find a comfortable open floor plan with gas fireplace downstairs, a single car attached garage. Upstairs you'll find a spacious primary suite with 2 additional bedrooms and full shared bath. The backyard has a floating deck and a great space for entertaining family and friends. Call to schedule your showing today!
